                    <div class="blog-tags"></div><div class="blog-category"><a href="http://www.rawstory.com/rs/category/trigger-happy/" title="View all posts in Trigger Happy">Trigger Happy</a></div><div class="clear"></div><h1 class="blog-title">Who gets shot in America: What I learned compiling records of carnage for the New York Times</h1><div class="blog-author"><span class="head"></span> <a href="http://www.rawstory.com/rs/author/jennifermascia/" title="Posts by Jennifer Mascia" rel="author">Jennifer Mascia</a><br><a href="http://www.rawstory.com/rs/2014/07/15/" >15 Jul 2014</a>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</div><div class="clear"></div><div class="share-container">                        <div class="addthis_responsive_sharing"></div>
                        <div class='clear'></div></div>                    
                    
                    <div class="follow-appeal-container">
                        <div class="appeal">Don't miss stories. Follow Raw Story!</div>
                        <div class="icons">
