                    <li>
                        <a href="http://www.rawstory.com/rs/2014/09/it-belongs-to-god-pat-robertson-snaps-at-liberal-viewer-who-wants-to-tax-churches/" title="&#8216;It belongs to God!&#8217;: Pat Robertson snaps at &#8216;liberal&#8217; viewer who wants to tax churches" target="_self"><img src="http://www.rawstory.com/rs/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/cbn_700club_taxes_140922a-300x161.jpg" class="rpc-thumbnail" alt=""/></a>
                        <a href="http://www.rawstory.com/rs/2014/09/it-belongs-to-god-pat-robertson-snaps-at-liberal-viewer-who-wants-to-tax-churches/" title="&#8216;It belongs to God!&#8217;: Pat Robertson snaps at &#8216;liberal&#8217; viewer who wants to tax churches" class="rpc-post-title" target="_self">&#8216;It belongs to God!&#8217;: Pat Robertson snaps at &#8216;liberal&#8217; viewer who wants to tax churches</a>
                        <div class="clear"></div>
                        <div id="rpc_share_656448" class="rpc-share-count">0 <img src="http://www.rawstory.com/rs/wp-content/themes/worldwide-v1-02/images/shares.jpg"></div>
                        <script type='text/javascript'>jQuery(document).ready(function(){ get_share_stats( 'http://www.rawstory.com/rs/2014/09/it-belongs-to-god-pat-robertson-snaps-at-liberal-viewer-who-wants-to-tax-churches/', '#rpc_share_656448', '<img src="http://www.rawstory.com/rs/wp-content/themes/worldwide-v1-02/images/shares.jpg">' ); });</script>
